  <summary date="2020-04-10T18:19:32Z" status="Introduced in House">Enewetak Atoll Cleanup Radiation Study Act

This bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs to seek to enter an agreement with the National Academies of Sciences, Engineering, and Medicine to conduct a study and report on the level of radiation exposure experienced by members of the Armed Forces who participated in the cleanup of Enewetak Atoll between January 1, 1977, and December 31, 1980.</summary>
